	In this publication, we address these questions and set out a number of possible futures for schools <br />
	and schooling systems. Our goal is not to generate a single ‘preferred future’, or to offer any kind of <br />
	prediction, but to contribute to the ongoing debate about future schools by helping to extend the time <br />
	horizons within which that debate occurs, and by identifying the possible implications of strategic <br />
	choices that school leaders, policy-makers and others could make in the coming decade. 
